Class Domain

  • java.lang.Object
    • field.FieldElement
      • field.Property
        • field.Domain
  • public class Domain
extends Property
    A Domain represents a property object that has a rent that has to be payed by an other player if they step by it and the domain is it represents the streets that a player can buy in the Monopoly.
